The paper focuses on detecting anomalous behavior in computer and network logs using unsupervised neural network language models. This falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) as well as machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) and possibly social and information networks (cs.SI) as the approach involves modeling sequences of users' actions over time.
